# ============================================
# .cursorignore - Cursor IDE 索引排除规则
# 作用：减少 Cursor 后台索引任务，降低 CPU/内存占用
# 注意：不影响 Git 提交（与 .gitignore 独立）
# ============================================

# --- 依赖目录 ---
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# --- 编译输出与 Source Map ---
*.map
dist/
build/
out/
coverage/

# --- 缓存目录 ---
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
.ruff_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
.ralph/
**/.ralph/
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.eslintcache/
.parcel-cache/
.next/
.nuxt/
.svelte-kit/

# --- IDE 配置（子项目中的副本不需要索引）---
.vscode/
.idea/
**/.cursor
**/.codex
**/.vibe
**/.hermes
**/.claude-plugin
**/.codex-plugin

# --- 第三方 Agent/IDE 配置目录（冗余副本）---
**/.agents
**/.kiro
**/.opencode
**/.codebuddy
**/.qwen
**/.trae
**/.zed
**/.gemini

# --- 自动生成索引文件（运行时搜索用，不需要索引内容）---
skill-index.json
skill-index-temp.json
cli-index.json
cli-manifest.json
**/skills-index.json

# --- 日志与临时文件 ---
*.log
*.tmp
*.temp
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.zip

# --- 系统文件 ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# --- 工作区（用户数据，非代码）---
workspace/

# --- 子项目特定排除 ---
subprojects/OpenCLI/extension/dist/
subprojects/OpenCLI/extension/out/
subprojects/OpenCLI/*.vsix
subprojects/everything-claude-code/manifests/
